title: Vaeda - State of Nature & Asleep at the Wheel EP - TPB Exclusive
description:
Vaeda is a band of New York. Their first CD, State Of Nature, and their newest EP, Asleep at the Wheel, are included. The band has 3 members: Ian Lear (Vocals), Oliver Williams (Drums), and Aristotle Dreher (Bass). This is a must checkout for any rock fan. Look them up on MySpace to find out more!
